item.description:
Anyone interested in hiking Wednesday afternoon?
We meet at Dartmouth Skiway parking lot in Lyme. Depart from the Skiway parking lot, on foot, to the trailhead. Begin our hike @4:00pm.
Bring a headlamp just in case. I’ve hiked Holt’s ledge in the past but never in the dark. It will be an adventure if it is dark before we step out of the woods.

group.name: Lebanon/White River Junction Hiking Meetup Group
